## 🌍 Solution Challenge Goal

This project supports the **UN Sustainable Development Goal (SDG 3)**:  
> *“Good Health and Well-being” – Ensure healthy lives and promote well-being for all at all ages.*

By providing a safe, anonymous, and AI-powered space, **Secret Talk** helps users express themselves, reflect on their emotions, and receive support in a non-judgmental way.

